      ******************************************************************
      *   DIRECTOR WORKFLOW                                            *
      ******************************************************************
       VIAP3001-WORKFLOW.
      *
           CALL 'VIAR3001' USING ETCL0002-COMMAREA,
                                 VIAL3001-DATA
             ON EXCEPTION
               SET VIAL0002-ERROS-ARQ    TO TRUE
               MOVE VIAK0001-PROG-NOTFND TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
               MOVE VIAK0002-APLIC-AT    TO VIAL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO
           END-CALL.
      *
       VIAP3001-WORKFLOW-EXIT.
           EXIT.
